name: Static Storm (Lapwell)
description:
Just a little thing me and a co-worker made for the Trijam 196 "Interference does damage." For a my first time ever using Typescript and Phaser, I think it turned out quite well!

Shout out to my co-worker for helping out and even doing this jam with me :) Check out his itch.io, his stuff is waaay better than mine lol.
